Feedback needed: Student Code of Conduct

We need your feedback! We are developing a new Student Code of Conduct to create greater clarity and consistency in our practices. Please provide input on the draft document either online or in person. Click on the title to learn more.

WPS Rally on the River 2024

On Aug. 6 we welcomed all WPS employees to the Rally on the River at Riverfront Stadium to kick off the school year and launch our new strategic plan.

Wichita Park and Recreation and Wichita Public Schools announce partnership

Wichitaâ€™s Park and Recreation Department and Wichita Public Schools have announced a collaboration to enhance the Wichita Junior Football League and sharing facilities.

WPS and DOJ settlement agreement

The Wichita Public Schools and the U.S. Department of Justice reached an agreement following an investigation that began in the spring of 2022.

WPS creates Wichita Public Schools Foundation

The district has announced the creation of an education foundation to raise funds to remove barriers and provide opportunities to the students and staff of Wichita Public Schools.
